name: For Sail
description: I have a habit of taking any interesting photos, when I get home from a photo job and under the scorching heat of a tropical country, even though the conditions are wet and dry, but when I see a ship sitting on the shore, without thinking, I immediately take the camera out of my bag and can only see took 1 picture because the battery turned out to be limited, and here it is, FOR SAIL, one of the photos from my bucketlist which is my favorite photo so far.
